<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-564-704  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 564 704.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  June 19 1990 v4 n23 p22(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Coastal Associates Publishing L.P. 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>On Location bundled with MacAvenue Protege drives. (productannouncement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Farber, Daniel.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   CompuAdd Corp. MacAvenue Corp. (product introduction)ON Technology Inc. (products).andO;Product:   On Location (File mangement software) (marketing)MacAvenue Protege (Hard disk drive) (product introduction).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionDisk DrivesBundled Software.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>By Daniel FarberandM;Austin, Texas -- Mail-order distributor MacAvenue last week announced plansto sell its own line of external hard drives and bundle them with OnLocation, the file-finding utility from ON Technology Inc.andM;The new, aggressively priced Protege series, slated to begin shipping July 1,was developed for MacAvenue by its parent company, CompuAdd Corp., which lastyear shipped more than 150,000 drives for the MS-DOS market.andM;The units, which range in capacity from 20 to 100 Mbytes, are available witheither Seagate or Quantum mechanisms.andP;  They are packaged in a shoe box-shapedcase that is about 4.4 inches high, 5 inches wide and 9.4 inches deep.andO;Inside the ribbed plastic exterior is a metal chassis engineered to ensurequiet operation and isolate the drive mechanism from electrostatic discharge,according to Michael Shapiro, MacAvenue product manager.andM;The drives will be shipped with Protege Disk Management Software, allowingusers to create and password-protect partitions, including Unix and ProDOSpartitions, which can be modified without reformatting the disk.andP;  Thesoftware supports disk spanning, which makes multiple compatible drivesappear as one volume.andP;  A Control Panel device (cdev) lets users partition andmount volumes.andM;The company said that it will have exclusive rights to the $129.95 programfor six months, as part of a one-year contract to bundle On Location with allProtege drives.andM;MacAvenue provides overnight shipping for $2, a one-year limited warranty anda 30-day money-back guarantee.andM;MacAvenue is located at 12303 Technology Blvd., Austin, Texas 78727; (512)331-0446; (800) 388-6221.andO;</TEXT></DOC>